<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> We do not support the destruction of the environment. That is a blanket statement that is based on a false assumption. We view the environment, and any destruction of the environment, as a property rights issue. Any action that damages the property of others is wrong, and you can be held liable for it.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
