<br>
Although many of the arguments Marx came up with against capitalism are actually quite sound although usualy only against the more extreme forms.<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>  What does a rich person need a public hospital for?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
