<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>  But that isn't really the point.  Desert Storm wasn't only protecting the rich, it was protecting everyone's oil supply. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
